user_description: Working to improve health and care for Enfield as part of north central London clinical commissioning group (@NHS_NCLCCG). Monitored Mon - Fri, 9am - 5pm.
text:
You can get your #CovidVaccine at Evergreen Surgery’s walk-in Pfizer and AstraZeneca vaccination clinic on Mon-Sun at 9am - 6pm.

No booking needed. Everyone aged 16+ can get a jab. Second doses given 8 weeks after the 1st.

Find out more: https://t.co/g1PCnom7uQ https://t.co/o3bUpLiwFD
